The '''''Toorna's Profits''''' was a [[Freighter/Legends|freighter]] that landed on [[Vogga]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt's]] dock on [[Nar Shaddaa/Legends|Nar Shaddaa]]. The landing was delayed however, due to a mix-up of the ID signatures of the ''Toorna's Profits'', the ''[[Silver Zephyr]]'', and the ''[[Alakandor]]''.

[[Fassa (Twi'lek)|Fassa]], the dock manager, asked the [[Meetra Surik|Jedi Exile]] to correct this. With a little tinkering, the Exile distributed power to the three pylons and assigned priorities for the ships as follows:
*1st: ''Silver Zephyr''
*2nd: ''Alakandor''
*3rd: ''Toorna's Profits''

